This movie is a standard late night erotic film. The movie stars Kelly Brown as a secretary at a company which has some shady dealings going on. One of the top executive\&#039;s (Dale Debone) secretary\&#039;s has been fired and everyone is after the job. When the least qualified woman (Adult film actress Jamie Sweet) gets the job, it becomes apparent she got it by sleeping around and she may be in cahoots with someone regarding possible embezzlement. Kelly along with another secretary (Alana Evans) and an accountant (Chris Evans) at the company join forces to try to solve the mystery. The acting in the film is OK, nothing special and the script is not that great either. There are a lot of sex scenes and nudity in this film which should satisfy fans of erotic films. Not the best movie but passable.
